## Installation

### From Claude Code marketplace
```bash
/plugin marketplace add <marketplace-url>
/plugin install {{ name }}
```

### From GitHub
```bash
# Skills only (cross-agent)
npx skills add richfrem/agent-plugins-skills --path plugins/{{ name }}

# Full plugin (Claude Code native)
/plugin marketplace add richfrem/agent-plugins-skills
/plugin install {{ name }}
```

### Local development (settings.json)
Add to your `.claude/settings.json` for reliable local discovery on all platforms:
```json
{
  "plugins": [
    {
      "source": "settings",
      "path": "./plugins/{{ name }}"
    }
  ]
}
```
Then run `/reload-plugins` to activate without restarting.

