## Dependencies

By default, standard library dependencies are assumed. If external packages are required,
declare them in `requirements.in` and use the standard `pip-compile` workflow:

```bash
cd plugins/{{ name }}
pip-compile requirements.in
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

